      This fits your .

    • High-speed 20W PD Fast Charger: UGREEN USB C car charger supports the fast charging of your devices. With a power of up to 20W at the PD connection, you can achieve the desired quick-charging effect for your PD-enabled devices. It can fully charge your cell Phone device 60% in 35 minutes.

        Product description

        UGREEN 20W Super Fast and Super Mini PD&QC3.0 Car Charger:

        High-speed 20W PD Fast Charger: UGREEN USB C car fast charger supports the fast charging of your devices. With a power of up to 20W at the PD connection, you achieve the desired quick-charging effect for your PD-enabled devices. It can fully charge the Cell Phone device 60% in 35 minutes.

        Dual-port charging: Equipped with 20W Power Delivery USB C Charger and 18W Qualcomm Quick Charge Charger(Total power 24W), UGREEN cigarette lighter usb charger can charge two devices simultaneously. Built-in smart chips automatically assign power to each port when two devices are charged to prevent your devices from being damaged by the massive power input.

        Premium metal material: The housing made of an all-aluminum alloy offers better scratch resistance, heat dissipation, an attractive design, and long service life. It does not take up space; it is perfectly suitable for all 12V/24V small cars and large truck sockets.

        Universal compatibility: Compatible with most usb powered devices like iPhone 12/11/ 11 Pro/SE, iPad Pro/Air/Mini, SAMSUNG S10/ S9/ S8/ S7/Note 10/Note 20 Ultra/10/Plus/9/8, XIAOMI REDMI Note 8/ 7/ Mi 9/ Mi 8, MOTO G7/ G6/ Z,Nintendo Switch, Tomtom Sat Nav, Garmin SatNav, Dash Cam and more.

        Safe and intelligent: Built-in Power management chip, the UGREEN car phone charger not only offers fast charging speed but also prevents your devices from being exposed to overvoltage, overcurrent, short circuit, etc. Circuit and is not overheated at high temperatures.

        Product Description

        Charge Fast, Charge Safer. UGREEN car charger brings you a more convenient life.

        2-Port USB with 20WPD3.0 and 18WQC3.0

        1. When only 1 devices connected, both USB ports of this mini car charger support QC 3.0/2.0, AFC, FCP fast charge protocols. In addition, the USB C port also supports PD 3.0/2.0.

        2. When 2 devices connected, this car charger will charge them simultaneously with total 24w maximum output.

        Kindly Reminder: Both USB ports will charge Huawei SCP & FCP phones at 5V/2A or 9V/2A since FCP only support maximum 2A charge current.

        Innovative High-Speed Charging

        UGREEN Fast Car Charger can fully charge the Cell Phone device 60% in 35 minutes and fully charge the mobile phone in 1 ~ 1.5 hours.

        Read more

        Super Fast Car Charger

        With the support of the latest PD Fast Charge technology, the USB C port of UGREEN USB C Car Charger can quickly charge new iPhones and other PD-enabled devices much faster than the 5V/1A adapter. In addition, it also complies with QC 3.0/2.0 FCP AFC fast charge protocols.

        Smart Multi-protection Chip

        UGREEN cigarette lighter usb charger can effectively protect against overcharge/ overpressure/ over-heating / over-current / short-circuiting, ensuring the safety of you and your devices.

        Compatible with Almost All Motor Vehicles

        12V-24V wide range input, suitable for cars, SUVs, trucks and almost all the vehicles.

        Read more

        Faster Heat Dissipation

        Unlike many plastic car chargers, this charger is made of Fireproof Aluminum Alloy to maximize your safety.Good heat resistance makes your charging safer.

        Fearless of Bumps

        Dont be afraid of bumps even when driving on rough roads. Spring contact design can ensure the stability of the charger.

        Perfect Fit for Your Car

        The usb c car charger will not block anything near the cigarette lighter socket unlike a larger cell phone charger; Edge ridge design provides easy insertion and removal from vehicle lighter socket.
